title: 176. Nicole Hayes & Adrian Beck: Little Legends
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary: Award winning author and fellow podcaster joins best-selling children's author and sometimes co-host Adrian Beck to chat about their AFL branded book Little Legends. They chat to Dani Vee about diversity, the importance of community, collaborating, AFL and what we can achieve in a year if we put our minds to it. Listen now.
